<td class="d-block comment-body markdown-body  js-comment-body">

          <h4>Description</h4>
<p>Add options for Markdown syntax, Plain syntax, LinkBox special file, ToDo syntax, that allow to specify text to be appended.</p>
<p>Also allow to specify some variables/dynamics. A Jekyll user may know liquid date syntax, which I do prefer for resolving this.</p>
<p>Currently this is:</p>
<ul>
<li>Date:  <code>{{ date: "dateformat" }}</code></li>
<li>May be extended. date most important</li>
</ul>
<p>For ToDo use as default: <code>{{ date: "dateformat" }}</code></p>
